{"id":8568,"date":"2025-09-22T10:55:46","date_gmt":"2025-09-22T10:55:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=8568"},"modified":"2025-10-14T11:55:12","modified_gmt":"2025-10-14T11:55:12","slug":"rann-utsav-special","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/rann-utsav-special\/","title":{"rendered":"RANN UTSAV SPECIAL"},"content":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8836,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[103],"activities":[],"trip_types":[75],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[77],"class_list":["post-8568","trip","type-trip","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","destination-explore-gujarat","trip_types-customized-domestic-tour","tripcategory-customized-domestic-tour"],"packages_ids":[8573],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-8568","price":18777,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":3,"nights":2,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Celebrate the magic of Gujarat\u2019s most iconic festival with the <strong>Rann Utsav Special<\/strong> tour. Set in the breathtaking <strong>White Desert of Kutch<\/strong>, this vibrant cultural extravaganza showcases the best of Gujarat\u2019s art, craft, music, dance, and cuisine under the shimmering full moon. Stay in traditional tents, enjoy folk performances, shop for colorful handicrafts, and witness the desert transform into a glowing wonderland at night. Along with the festival, explore the <strong>historic town of Bhuj<\/strong>, the grand <strong>Aina Mahal and Prag Mahal<\/strong>, and nearby villages renowned for their embroidery and handicrafts. With its perfect mix of culture, tradition, and natural beauty, the Rann Utsav offers an unforgettable experience of Gujarat\u2019s rich heritage in a once-in-a-lifetime setting.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","cost_includes":" 3 star premium hotel stay\n All transfers and sightseeing by AC Vehicle\n This cost valid for 6 adults traveling together\n Breakfast, Dinner\n Toll Tax\n Parking\n Driver Allowance\nTravel Goodies\n 24 x 7 On tour Assistance\n All cost from EX Destination","cost_excludes":" Any meals other than those mentioned above in inclusions\n Airfare \/ Train Ticket\n GST 5%\n All monument entry Fees\n Any portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all items of personal nature\n Any services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions\nEntrance fees to Monuments & other sightseeing points\nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle malfunctions, political disturbances, etc.\nAnything not mentioned in inclusions","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What is the Rann Utsav?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Rann Utsav is a cultural festival held in the White Desert of Kutch, showcasing Gujarat\u2019s folk music, dance, handicrafts, cuisine, and traditions.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. When does the Rann Utsav take place? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is usually celebrated from November to February, with the best experience during full moon nights.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. Where is the Rann Utsav held? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It takes place in the Great Rann of Kutch, primarily in and around Dhordo village.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"4. What are the highlights of the festival?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Moonlit views of the white salt desert, cultural performances, camel rides, adventure sports, handicraft bazaars, and traditional cuisine.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"5. What type of accommodation is available? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tourists stay in luxury and standard tented accommodations at the Rann Utsav tent city, with modern amenities and cultural decor.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{"width":374,"height":226,"file":"2025\/09\/rann-utsav-special-1.png","filesize":120118,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"rann-utsav-special-1-300x181.png","width":300,"height":181,"filesize":48251,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rann-utsav-special-1-300x181.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"rann-utsav-special-1-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":24326,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rann-utsav-special-1-150x150.png"},"blog-sidebar-size":{"file":"rann-utsav-special-1-100x100.png","width":100,"height":100,"filesize":6925,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rann-utsav-special-1-100x100.png"},"blog-sidebar-size-thumb":{"file":"rann-utsav-special-1-90x80.png","width":90,"height":80,"filesize":9860,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rann-utsav-special-1-90x80.png"},"blog-post-two":{"file":"rann-utsav-special-1-342x226.png","width":342,"height":226,"filesize":67896,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/rann-utsav-special-1-342x226.png"},"travolo-related-post-size":{"file":"rann-utsav-special-1-270x226.png","width":270,"height":226,"filesize":56774,"mime_type":"image